<strong>MODIS:</strong> Moderate Resolution Imaging
Spectroradiometer.<br/>
<strong>MSAVI:</strong> Modified Soil Adjusted Vegetation Index.
<strong>NBR:</strong> Normalised Burn Ratio. <strong>NBRT:</strong>
Normalised Burn Ratio Thermal. <strong>NDVI:</strong> Normalised
Difference Vegetation Index.<br/>
<strong>NDVIT:</strong> Normalised Difference Vegetation Index Thermal.
<strong>NDWI:</strong> Normalised Difference Water Index.
<strong>RdNBR:</strong> Relativised Differenced Normalised Burn
Ratio.<br/>
<strong>RdFCT:</strong> Relativised Differenced Total Fraction Cover.
<strong>SPOT2:</strong> Satellite pour l'Observation de la Terre.
<strong>UAV:</strong> Unmanned Aerial Vehicle. <strong>VARI:</strong>
Visible Atmospherically Resistant Index.<br/>
<strong>VI6T:</strong> Vegetation Index 6 Thermal.</p>
